Description: Python API for the Playwright browser automation library (Avalan PPA pin)
 Playwright is a Microsoft-maintained library for browser automation
 that exposes a single async/sync API across Chromium, Firefox, and
 WebKit. This rebuild ships the pure-Python client at 1.55.0 because
 Avalan tracks `>= 1.54, < 2.0`; Noble's archive does not carry a
 matching version. The bundled browser drivers and pre-built browser
 binaries from upstream's wheels are deliberately not built -- users
 install chromium (or firefox) via apt separately, and Playwright
 falls back to those system browsers at runtime.
